title: John Denver Discography Part 10
description:
PART 10 - SERIOUSLY! YOU DO NOT NEED THIS!

Ok Ok - I put in all the rest of the stuff I&#039;ve found on bittorrent - and improved - I have tagged it all, cover art, even lyrics (IN THE TAGS). So it is better than the stuff that has been on bittorrent forever. But YOU DON&#039;T NEED IT. I included what you need in Parts 1-8, this is just stuff you (and I) will find when you search bittorrent. It&#039;s extra. Believe me! But I know you won&#039;t so here it is. But given these caveats, I don&#039;t know how long *I* will seed this since it is bittorrent available - AND redundant. But - hey - I WAS trying to supercede all the old stuff. I&#039;ll support this for a while - but if you get it, seed it, because I will drop this as soon as I get an inkling to do so.

SO - just in case - put on "high priority" the pieces you want, because you MAY not get it all. I&#039;ll try, but no promises.
